(44, 16, 5, 49, 4, 13, 16, 'increased in number daily', 'Growth and Unity in Faith', 'Both passages emphasize the growth of the church and the establishment of faith. Acts 16:5 mentions churches increasing in number, while Ephesians 4:13-16 speaks of growing into the fullness of Christ, highlighting the importance of unity and maturity in faith.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 16, 5, 60, 5, 10, 10, 'established in the faith', 'Establishment and Strengthening in Faith', 'This connection highlights the theme of being established and strengthened in faith. Acts 16:5 mentions churches being established, while 1 Peter 5:10 speaks of God making believers perfect and stablishing them.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 16, 5, 45, 16, 25, 25, 'established in the faith', 'Establishment in Faith', 'This connection highlights the theme of being established in faith. Both passages emphasize the strengthening of believers through the gospel and the preaching of Jesus Christ.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 16, 5, 46, 15, 58, 58, 'increased in number daily', 'Faith and Labor in the Lord', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of steadfastness and growth in faith. Acts highlights the establishment and increase of churches, while Corinthians encourages believers to be steadfast in their work, assuring them that their labor is not in vain.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(44, 16, 5, 51, 2, 6, 6, 'established in the faith', 'Establishment in Faith and Walking', 'This connection highlights the theme of growth in faith. Acts 16:5 mentions being established in faith, while Colossians 2:6 encourages believers to walk in Christ, suggesting a continuous growth and deepening of faith.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
